strings.Value: "Very well, Nok-Nok. Here's your chance to get even."
"No, Nok-Nok. I'll deal with the chieftain myself."
"How do you intend to fight him?"
"I hope you know what you're doing..."
"Stop! Stop! I smash this shatshanks alone!"
"I can't sleep knowing this ratbag wears the crown! He wanted to hit me until me dead! Now I hit him and show whole tribe who {g|Lamashtu}Lamashtu{/g} chooses!"

"Like true goblin, like goblin Hero!" {n}Nok-Nok grins widely, showing his sharp teeth.{/n} "Fight with anything I have, anyhow I can! Bite, kick, stab, stick… maybe bite again — those are rules. Watch — see for self!"

{n}Nok-Nok hisses — presumably pleased.{/n} "Good! Cheer for me then!"{n} He pauses, then narrows his eyes at you and leans in with a whisper.{/n} "But hsst — try to speak good so they know you cheering for me. You always mess up your words."

"Hnh! Just don't trip me up — and stay out of my way!" {n}Nok-Nok waves his hand, as if dismissing you.{/n} "Maybe you go talk-talk with them before I punch and kick crown-stealing shatshank, but after that — stay away! Now enough talk, let's go — look, there — that's where shatshanks hides!"
